# Project Description

This project demonstrates the implementation of a **Security Operations Center (SOC) monitoring environment** using **Wazuh SIEM**.

The goal of this lab is to build a centralized monitoring system capable of:

• Collecting security logs from endpoints
• Detecting suspicious activities
• Generating security alerts
• Mapping detected threats using the **MITRE ATT&CK framework**

The SOC environment analyzes logs collected from monitored systems and visualizes the results through the Wazuh Dashboard.

