# SOC Components

## Wazuh Manager

The Wazuh Manager is the central component responsible for analyzing logs received from endpoint agents.

Main functions:

• Log analysis
• Threat detection
• Security alert generation
• Incident monitoring

---

## Wazuh Agent

The Wazuh Agent runs on endpoint systems and collects system logs.

Functions include:

• System log collection
• File integrity monitoring
• Suspicious activity detection
• Event reporting to the Wazuh Manager

---

## Wazuh Dashboard

The Wazuh Dashboard provides a graphical interface used by security analysts to monitor alerts and analyze threats.

Dashboard features:

• Security event visualization
• Agent monitoring
• MITRE ATT&CK mapping
• Threat investigation

